1
00:00:07,007 --> 00:00:11,678
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, my God, I cannot fucking believe this.
Here we fucking go!</font>

2
00:00:11,762 --> 00:00:13,055
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, jeez.</font>

3
00:00:14,973 --> 00:00:18,310
<font face="Serif" size="18">Pardon the interruption.
We are once again in the federal clear.</font>

4
00:00:18,393 --> 00:00:20,812
<font face="Serif" size="18">Rick, what the hell?
Are you a Turkey Dracula now?</font>

5
00:00:20,896 --> 00:00:22,523
<font face="Serif" size="18">Morty, is that a Pooplickian GamePod?</font>

6
00:00:22,606 --> 00:00:24,191
<font face="Serif" size="18">Actually it's the GamePod XL.</font>

7
00:00:24,274 --> 00:00:26,652
<font face="Serif" size="18">They say it's the most realistic
video-game console ever.</font>

8
00:00:26,735 --> 00:00:28,445
<font face="Serif" size="18">- I never got you that.
- Space Mom did.</font>

9
00:00:28,529 --> 00:00:30,364
<font face="Serif" size="18">She's in for the holiday weekend. Remember?</font>

10
00:00:30,447 --> 00:00:33,700
<font face="Serif" size="18">- In that case, let's go, let's get out--
- [Beth] I heard you smack the glass,</font>

11
00:00:33,784 --> 00:00:37,120
<font face="Serif" size="18">- if you bail, I'll disown you!
- [Space Beth] I'd say don't hop through a portal.</font>

12
00:00:37,204 --> 00:00:38,539
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wait, you can't.</font>

13
00:00:38,622 --> 00:00:39,831
<font face="Serif" size="18">Look at it this way, Morty.</font>

14
00:00:39,915 --> 00:00:43,377
<font face="Serif" size="18">Life is a subscription
and Thanksgiving is your family's yearly charge.</font>

15
00:00:43,460 --> 00:00:45,337
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wow, Dad, good job.</font>

16
00:00:45,420 --> 00:00:47,798
<font face="Serif" size="18">Rick, put some pants on.</font>

17
00:00:47,881 --> 00:00:49,675
<font face="Serif" size="18">Today has so few rules.</font>

18
00:00:49,758 --> 00:00:51,009
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yes, Patriarch.</font>

19
00:00:52,511 --> 00:00:53,470
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ding, ding, ding!</font>

20
00:00:53,554 --> 00:00:54,930
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'd like to make a toast.</font>

21
00:00:55,013 --> 00:00:57,516
<font face="Serif" size="18">Today is a day for thanks.</font>

22
00:00:57,599 --> 00:00:59,434
<font face="Serif" size="18">And for family.</font>

23
00:00:59,518 --> 00:01:02,104
<font face="Serif" size="18">And for remembering
all of those that have less.</font>

24
00:01:02,187 --> 00:01:04,273
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Okay, pick a scope.
- Pick a scope?</font>

25
00:01:04,356 --> 00:01:06,149
<font face="Serif" size="18">Can we please have a normal Thanksgiving?</font>

26
00:01:06,233 --> 00:01:08,944
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Seems like all the ones I remember.
- Good point.</font>

27
00:01:09,611 --> 00:01:13,282
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Baby, you, it's a toast--
- [both] Sorry!</font>

28
00:01:15,158 --> 00:01:18,078
<font face="Serif" size="18">Anyway, I'm thankful for my wife.</font>

29
00:01:18,161 --> 00:01:20,038
<font face="Serif" size="18">Beth. The Beth that chose me.</font>

30
00:01:20,122 --> 00:01:24,751
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm so grateful to you
and I literally could not live without you.</font>

31
00:01:24,835 --> 00:01:26,253
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Aw.
- I really mean that.</font>

32
00:01:26,336 --> 00:01:28,880
<font face="Serif" size="18">If something were to happen to you
or if you were to leave me</font>

33
00:01:28,964 --> 00:01:31,008
<font face="Serif" size="18">or be unfaithful, I would die.</font>

34
00:01:31,091 --> 00:01:34,011
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Literally. Probably by my own hand.
- Okay.</font>

35
00:01:34,094 --> 00:01:35,304
<font face="Serif" size="18">I know how I'd do it.</font>

36
00:01:35,387 --> 00:01:37,180
<font face="Serif" size="18">Our first blender has an extra-long cord</font>

37
00:01:37,264 --> 00:01:39,224
<font face="Serif" size="18">and it was manufactured
before safety fuses,</font>

38
00:01:39,308 --> 00:01:40,726
<font face="Serif" size="18">so I'd draw a warm bath...</font>

39
00:01:40,809 --> 00:01:44,104
<font face="Serif" size="18">And blend some stuff. Good toast, honey.
To thankfulness.</font>

40
00:01:44,187 --> 00:01:46,064
<font face="Serif" size="18">To America?</font>

41
00:01:46,148 --> 00:01:47,441
<font face="Serif" size="18">To ending the toast?</font>

42
00:01:47,524 --> 00:01:49,318
<font face="Serif" size="18">[all] To ending the toast!</font>

43
00:01:49,401 --> 00:01:52,738
<font face="Serif" size="18">Just to be clear, I was saying I'd kill myself.</font>

44
00:01:52,821 --> 00:01:54,531
<font face="Serif" size="18">- God, we know.
- God.</font>

45
00:01:54,615 --> 00:01:55,866
<font face="Serif" size="18">[theme music playing]</font>

46
00:02:26,980 --> 00:02:28,649
<font face="Serif" size="18">Sorry, Jerry got all husband-y.</font>

47
00:02:28,732 --> 00:02:30,525
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah, do not miss that.</font>

48
00:02:30,609 --> 00:02:33,028
<font face="Serif" size="18">I was thinking we could set you up
in Jerry's man cave?</font>

49
00:02:33,111 --> 00:02:34,154
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'll sleep in my car.</font>

50
00:02:34,237 --> 00:02:36,531
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's got a Tardis thing going on,
bigger on the inside.</font>

51
00:02:36,615 --> 00:02:40,160
<font face="Serif" size="18">Dad calls it hack,
but my soaking tub begs to differ.</font>

52
00:02:40,243 --> 00:02:41,787
<font face="Serif" size="18">Maybe I'll trade you.</font>

53
00:02:41,870 --> 00:02:42,871
<font face="Serif" size="18">[grunting]</font>

54
00:02:42,954 --> 00:02:45,457
<font face="Serif" size="18">- My lower back.
- Oh, I got this.</font>

55
00:02:45,540 --> 00:02:47,918
<font face="Serif" size="18">- [back cracks]
- Jesus, that was great.</font>

56
00:02:48,001 --> 00:02:49,461
<font face="Serif" size="18">Well, you're me.</font>

57
00:02:50,629 --> 00:02:53,298
<font face="Serif" size="18">I find this is usually the biggest help.</font>

58
00:02:54,132 --> 00:02:57,969
<font face="Serif" size="18">Mm. Oh, I just love the Venusian stuff.</font>

59
00:02:58,053 --> 00:03:00,514
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's cool, I get insecure trying
to pronounce this crap too</font>

60
00:03:00,597 --> 00:03:02,307
<font face="Serif" size="18">but I got just the thing for that.</font>

61
00:03:02,391 --> 00:03:03,475
<font face="Serif" size="18">Here.</font>

62
00:03:03,558 --> 00:03:05,185
<font face="Serif" size="18">[in Venusian]</font>

63
00:03:18,407 --> 00:03:20,909
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay, shoot that asteroid.
Now shoot that one.</font>

64
00:03:20,992 --> 00:03:22,869
<font face="Serif" size="18">Now shoot me in the face. This game's trash.</font>

65
00:03:22,953 --> 00:03:25,247
<font face="Serif" size="18">I didn't want to say anything,
but this does seem lame.</font>

66
00:03:25,330 --> 00:03:28,250
<font face="Serif" size="18">I thought it was maybe because
we've shot so many real asteroids.</font>

67
00:03:28,333 --> 00:03:30,752
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Let's look at the menu.
- There's the realism setting.</font>

68
00:03:30,836 --> 00:03:33,588
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh. Cool. Also stupid.
The factory setting is four?</font>

69
00:03:33,672 --> 00:03:36,550
<font face="Serif" size="18">- What do we want, 10?
- No, do nine, I'm kidding.</font>

70
00:03:36,633 --> 00:03:38,969
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Shut up, Summer.
- Shut up, Summer. Put 10.</font>

71
00:03:42,013 --> 00:03:43,056
<font face="Serif" size="18">This is the same.</font>

72
00:03:43,140 --> 00:03:44,975
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's worse. It's-- Oh, I get it.</font>

73
00:03:45,058 --> 00:03:46,601
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay. It's more real.</font>

74
00:03:46,685 --> 00:03:49,438
<font face="Serif" size="18">- The vast majority of space is empty.
- [Morty] What? Who cares?</font>

75
00:03:49,521 --> 00:03:50,939
<font face="Serif" size="18">Then what am I doing?</font>

76
00:03:51,022 --> 00:03:53,942
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Rick] Looks like you can record a video
for your kid in case you die.</font>

77
00:03:54,025 --> 00:03:57,571
<font face="Serif" size="18">Not a bad idea,
you're gonna be in space for a while.</font>

78
00:03:57,654 --> 00:03:58,697
<font face="Serif" size="18">May as well.</font>

79
00:03:58,780 --> 00:04:00,365
<font face="Serif" size="18">Um, hey. Son.</font>

80
00:04:00,449 --> 00:04:05,495
<font face="Serif" size="18">Uh, if you're seeing this, I starved to death
while looking for an asteroid.</font>

81
00:04:05,579 --> 00:04:07,372
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ugh. This is stupid.</font>

82
00:04:07,456 --> 00:04:09,624
<font face="Serif" size="18">You guys are trying
to convince yourselves it's cool</font>

83
00:04:09,708 --> 00:04:11,042
<font face="Serif" size="18">because you feel lame about it.</font>

84
00:04:11,126 --> 00:04:13,003
<font face="Serif" size="18">You know nothing about gamer culture.</font>

85
00:04:13,086 --> 00:04:15,797
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Bro, tell your son you love the shit out of him.
- Oh, I'm gonna!</font>

86
00:04:24,264 --> 00:04:26,975
<font face="Serif" size="18">Of course, we both can't sleep
at the same time.</font>

87
00:04:27,058 --> 00:04:29,060
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah, we do share a shitty back.</font>

88
00:04:29,144 --> 00:04:30,145
<font face="Serif" size="18">Turn around.</font>

89
00:04:30,228 --> 00:04:31,563
<font face="Serif" size="18">- At least let me--
- Yes, please.</font>

90
00:04:31,646 --> 00:04:33,231
<font face="Serif" size="18">- [back cracks]
- Oh, my God.</font>

91
00:04:33,315 --> 00:04:36,234
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay I know we're not massage people,
but you need this.</font>

92
00:04:36,318 --> 00:04:38,361
<font face="Serif" size="18">You act
like this badass space cowboy,</font>

93
00:04:38,445 --> 00:04:40,739
<font face="Serif" size="18">but I know you're just
a scared little overachiever</font>

94
00:04:40,822 --> 00:04:44,576
<font face="Serif" size="18">- that keeps all her OCD right--
- Oh, my God.</font>

95
00:04:44,659 --> 00:04:47,579
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah. By the way,
you better be taking notes. I'm next.</font>

96
00:04:47,662 --> 00:04:49,831
<font face="Serif" size="18">- It's my back, you dumb bitch.
- Nice.</font>

97
00:04:50,832 --> 00:04:51,708
<font face="Serif" size="18">What?</font>

98
00:04:57,005 --> 00:04:58,173
<font face="Serif" size="18">[clanging noise]</font>

99
00:05:00,217 --> 00:05:02,552
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Well, I better get back to bed.
- Yup. Same.</font>

100
00:05:07,557 --> 00:05:09,768
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, so now you're
into highly realistic video games?</font>

101
00:05:09,851 --> 00:05:12,354
<font face="Serif" size="18">Maybe I decided real life
was too much right now</font>

102
00:05:12,437 --> 00:05:14,731
<font face="Serif" size="18">or maybe I'm not afraid
to change my mind about stuff.</font>

103
00:05:14,815 --> 00:05:17,776
<font face="Serif" size="18">Maybe mental flexibility
is stronger than stubbornness.</font>

104
00:05:17,859 --> 00:05:19,444
<font face="Serif" size="18">Nice manip', Sum-Sum!</font>

105
00:05:19,528 --> 00:05:21,321
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay, I'm in the alley behind the library.</font>

106
00:05:21,404 --> 00:05:23,573
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Uptown or downtown?
- Shit, there's one uptown too?</font>

107
00:05:23,657 --> 00:05:25,242
<font face="Serif" size="18">I think I'm near the red line.</font>

108
00:05:25,325 --> 00:05:26,326
<font face="Serif" size="18">Is this <i>Street Fighter?</i></font>

109
00:05:26,409 --> 00:05:29,663
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Summer] <i>Street Fighterwhere</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> you start
at the beginning of each fighter's day</font>

110
00:05:29,746 --> 00:05:31,331
<font face="Serif" size="18">and have to find each other to fight.</font>

111
00:05:31,414 --> 00:05:34,668
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's realistic. Not guaranteed a fight will happen.
That meter filling up</font>

112
00:05:34,751 --> 00:05:36,336
<font face="Serif" size="18">is us forgetting what made us so mad.</font>

113
00:05:36,419 --> 00:05:39,005
<font face="Serif" size="18">If anyone's interested
in a higher level of realism,</font>

114
00:05:39,089 --> 00:05:40,924
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm booting up the O.G.</font>

115
00:05:41,007 --> 00:05:45,595
<font face="Serif" size="18">That's Original Game,
called a jigsaw puzzle, in the den.</font>

116
00:05:46,555 --> 00:05:48,557
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hey, gang!
Me and my space self are gonna</font>

117
00:05:48,640 --> 00:05:51,810
<font face="Serif" size="18">make a run to the Gloppy Drop System
for ice cream. Any flavor requests?</font>

118
00:05:51,893 --> 00:05:52,727
<font face="Serif" size="18">[both] Vanilla!</font>

119
00:05:52,811 --> 00:05:55,897
<font face="Serif" size="18">Why do you guys have to go all the way
to deep space just for ice cream?</font>

120
00:05:55,981 --> 00:05:58,275
<font face="Serif" size="18">Gloppy Dropulites
have less taste buds than humans.</font>

121
00:05:58,358 --> 00:06:00,110
<font face="Serif" size="18">Their ice cream is like a hospital bed.</font>

122
00:06:00,193 --> 00:06:02,445
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's designed for you to do less
so it does more.</font>

123
00:06:02,529 --> 00:06:03,989
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay see you in a bit.</font>

124
00:06:04,072 --> 00:06:07,033
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'll get started sorting
all the obvious sky pieces.</font>

125
00:06:07,117 --> 00:06:08,076
<font face="Serif" size="18">Secret technique.</font>

126
00:06:08,159 --> 00:06:10,078
<font face="Serif" size="18">- I'm gonna eat your ass!
- It's on!</font>

127
00:06:10,161 --> 00:06:12,247
<font face="Serif" size="18">You will die in the street like a dog!</font>

128
00:06:14,291 --> 00:06:15,709
<font face="Serif" size="18">[sighs]</font>

129
00:06:15,792 --> 00:06:16,960
<font face="Serif" size="18">Stunning.</font>

130
00:06:17,794 --> 00:06:18,962
<font face="Serif" size="18">Thank you.</font>

131
00:06:19,045 --> 00:06:20,714
<font face="Serif" size="18">This is incredible.</font>

132
00:06:20,797 --> 00:06:23,091
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Space Beth]
Just glad I had something in your size.</font>

133
00:06:23,174 --> 00:06:24,426
<font face="Serif" size="18">[both laughing]</font>

134
00:06:24,509 --> 00:06:26,177
<font face="Serif" size="18">How far is Gloppy Drop?</font>

135
00:06:26,261 --> 00:06:28,847
<font face="Serif" size="18">And why do I always think I'm wearing a watch?</font>

136
00:06:28,930 --> 00:06:32,225
<font face="Serif" size="18">I actually have a pint of Gloppy Drop
on a little apartment orbiting Earth.</font>

137
00:06:32,309 --> 00:06:33,518
<font face="Serif" size="18">So we have time.</font>

138
00:06:33,602 --> 00:06:35,520
<font face="Serif" size="18">You have your own space station?</font>

139
00:06:35,604 --> 00:06:37,188
<font face="Serif" size="18">We have our own space station.</font>

140
00:06:37,272 --> 00:06:38,481
<font face="Serif" size="18">We're the same person.</font>

141
00:06:38,565 --> 00:06:39,649
<font face="Serif" size="18">There's differences.</font>

142
00:06:39,733 --> 00:06:42,903
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Like, one of us has no idea who she really is.
- Wrong.</font>

143
00:06:42,986 --> 00:06:44,571
<font face="Serif" size="18">But let's make a deal.</font>

144
00:06:44,654 --> 00:06:47,949
<font face="Serif" size="18">Let's trust ourselves enough to stop wondering
who we are when we're together.</font>

145
00:06:48,033 --> 00:06:49,659
<font face="Serif" size="18">We get to say anything to each other.</font>

146
00:06:49,743 --> 00:06:52,621
<font face="Serif" size="18">Things we'd never say to anyone else,
even ourselves.</font>

147
00:06:52,704 --> 00:06:54,873
<font face="Serif" size="18">What don't we say to ourselves?</font>

148
00:06:54,956 --> 00:06:58,335
<font face="Serif" size="18">How about,
"Wow, my ass looks good in that space suit."</font>

149
00:06:58,418 --> 00:07:00,462
<font face="Serif" size="18">I mean it. I'm a good looking woman.</font>

150
00:07:00,545 --> 00:07:02,047
<font face="Serif" size="18">That's nice of you to say.</font>

151
00:07:02,130 --> 00:07:07,510
<font face="Serif" size="18">I also find myself quite attractive.</font>

152
00:07:16,811 --> 00:07:19,189
<font face="Serif" size="18">We forgot the ice cream.</font>

153
00:07:20,982 --> 00:07:24,486
<font face="Serif" size="18">I want you back in my guts
like I'm one of your sick little fillies.</font>

154
00:07:24,569 --> 00:07:25,779
<font face="Serif" size="18">[both moaning]</font>

155
00:07:32,577 --> 00:07:34,955
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, goddammit, Morty!
You can't just take my controller.</font>

156
00:07:35,038 --> 00:07:36,957
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yes I can! It's mine.</font>

157
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:38,333
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay, Sum-Sum, gimme.</font>

158
00:07:38,416 --> 00:07:41,544
<font face="Serif" size="18">Make your own controller,
some of us need all the control we can get.</font>

159
00:07:41,628 --> 00:07:42,545
<font face="Serif" size="18">Fuck you!</font>

160
00:07:43,588 --> 00:07:46,091
<font face="Serif" size="18">So why are you so suddenly
into realistic video games?</font>

161
00:07:46,174 --> 00:07:47,050
<font face="Serif" size="18">I already was.</font>

162
00:07:47,133 --> 00:07:49,094
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah, but now you're into them the way I am.</font>

163
00:07:49,177 --> 00:07:51,763
<font face="Serif" size="18">You mean like staring at them in a numb trance.</font>

164
00:07:51,846 --> 00:07:53,598
<font face="Serif" size="18">Not judging, just noticing.</font>

165
00:07:53,682 --> 00:07:56,309
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah, you tend to notice stuff
a little before I do.</font>

166
00:07:56,393 --> 00:07:57,727
<font face="Serif" size="18">Eventually, you do notice.</font>

167
00:07:57,811 --> 00:08:00,063
<font face="Serif" size="18">And now we can both
not notice together, yes.</font>

168
00:08:00,146 --> 00:08:02,107
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Jerry] Oh, my God. Beth?</font>

169
00:08:02,190 --> 00:08:04,317
<font face="Serif" size="18">I thought you said you got ice cream?</font>

170
00:08:04,401 --> 00:08:06,528
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Beth] Yeah I-- it must be in the...</font>

171
00:08:06,611 --> 00:08:08,613
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Space Beth] Oh, the car!
We left it in the car.</font>

172
00:08:08,697 --> 00:08:11,408
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Jerry] Okay, good!
'Cause that would have been weird!</font>

173
00:08:11,491 --> 00:08:13,702
<font face="Serif" size="18">I worry things might become
more and more noticeable.</font>

174
00:08:13,785 --> 00:08:16,079
<font face="Serif" size="18">If he kills himself,
